Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.14,0:01:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你拿到多少压岁钱了?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.16,0:01:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真岛应该有很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绵谷你拿到多少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.53,0:01:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十岁以上的人收圣诞礼物和压岁钱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.50,0:01:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法律是不允许的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.43,0:01:18.68,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz285.015\pos(211,296)\c&H172E20&}妈妈说的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.73,0:01:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你傻啊 那怎么可…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.56,0:01:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 太一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.34,0:01:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十岁以后就不能拿了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.11,0:01:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,违法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.21,0:01:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.24,0:01:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.84,0:01:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人也拿到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.66,0:01:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.18,0:01:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.18,0:01:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说回来 真岛拿了多少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.09,0:01:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.89,0:01:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十一万五千日元吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,违法!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.52,0:01:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯罪!
