Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:03.50,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(382,453)\frz18.92}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个说的都不是四字熟语吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小奏给人的印象是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「诗歌管弦」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}诗歌管弦（日语）：既懂汉诗与和歌，又懂乐器\N引申为文学和音乐都拿手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:06.18,writings3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz357.015\pos(186,499)}{\alpha&HE5}哦——
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.18,0:06:06.22,writings3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz357.015\pos(188,437)}{\alpha&HC5}哦——
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:06.26,writings3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz357.015\pos(190,397)}{\alpha&HA0}哦——
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:06.30,writings3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz357.015\pos(192,371)}{\alpha&H95}哦——
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:06.34,writings3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz357.015\pos(193,350)}{\alpha&H65}哦——
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:06.38,writings3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz357.015\pos(195,334)}{\alpha&H45}哦——
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:06.43,writings3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz357.015\pos(196,324)}{\alpha&H25}哦——
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.43,0:06:06.47,writings3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz357.015\pos(197,318)}{\alpha&H15}哦——
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:06.51,writings3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz357.015\pos(197,314)}{\alpha&H02}哦——
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:09.89,writings3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz357.015\pos(197,312)\fs33}哦——
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:09.89,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\c&H606367&\frz260.538\pos(248,433)}什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:09.89,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\c&H606367&\frz342.99\pos(244,498)}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 用那么美的词语形容我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 部长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.26,0:06:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要形容部长吗? 嗯嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「器…」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「器用贫乏」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}器用贫乏（日语）：什么事都能做点，但不成大器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的 部长…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想逗逗大家笑而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:30.66,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\c&H523D51&\an7\pos(794,77)\frz257.218}挺不错的啊 太一 \N说得很对嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:30.66,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an7\frz277.512\pos(241,58)\c&H3E3543&}这不是在伤口上撒盐吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:30.66,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an7\c&H3E3543&\pos(35,110)\frz281.886}你还真是「天衣无缝」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:30.66,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an7\c&H3E3543&\pos(59,290)\frz8.553}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺不错的啊太一 说得很对嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,器用贫乏…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的活动室就是这里啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我再三恳求女帝才拿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.17,0:06:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是杂物室嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且到处都是尘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么多意见嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且老师说了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「如果达到五个部员 就正式承认你们这个部」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「也给你们配指导老师」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的三个人 找不找得到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找到!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对能找到!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:06:59.90,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,むらさめの…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:06:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「骤雨…」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是歌留多?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌留多这东西…我怎么可能玩得来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.59,0:07:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本没那种天赋!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.46,0:07:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你不一样!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只会学习…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有书桌这一片天地啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.36,0:07:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要选同伴的话 比起歌留多的天才…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我更愿意选在榻榻米上 不断努力的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有经验的人就给我加入歌留多部啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加入吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:07:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有经验的人就给我加入歌留多部吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「因为凑齐了5个成员 所以请求正式成立歌留多部」…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.96,0:08:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.59,0:08:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部长要换成绫濑同学以外的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顾问暂时就由我来做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 解散
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:26.65,waka,,0000,0000,0000,,おとにきく…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「高师滨虽名…」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:29.49,waka,,0000,0000,0000,,ゆふされば…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「暮色沉田野…」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好快!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千早…这样果然还是不行啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实力相距太悬殊了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小奏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我刚开始玩歌留多的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对手也是个特别强的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他当时手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就不可能变得这么喜欢歌留多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我也不会手下留情的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:08:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.77,0:09:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想让大家变强
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暑假的时候我们五个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起去参加团体战的全国大会吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:11.40,subtitle_16_end,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(400,0)\c&H351B1F&}肉包T恤①
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:13.65,subtitle_16_end,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(400,0)\c&H351B1F&}肉包T恤②
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.24,0:09:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大碗!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:15.91,subtitle_16_end,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(400,0)\c&H351B1F&}肉包T恤③
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大大碗!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:23.54,subtitle_16_end,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(400,100)\c&H351B1F&}肉包T恤④
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特大碗!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉包小子他…在哪儿买的T恤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我姐姐喜欢丝网印刷 什么图案都能做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}即在丝网上覆盖镂空的图案，然后用可以\N渗透过网格的颜料把图案印上去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也让她帮你们俩做T恤吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:31.92,subtitle_16,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H2C2F42&\fs50\pos(303,437)}超大碗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不用啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不用麻烦了 好意心领了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}肉包小子真的不用啦 我们穿得普普通通就好…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我才不喜欢做这种衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.31,0:09:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有人苦苦央求我才做的啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 想做队服的话就告诉我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傲娇?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,批…批萨包子?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}包子里面放类似批萨的馅…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:56.20,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H264948&\frz266.622\pos(1084,126)}需要队服的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:56.20,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H264948&\frz347.445\pos(1088,225)}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:56.20,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H264948&\frz283.57\pos(901,363)}我给你们做好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:56.20,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H264948&\frz284.319\pos(877,405)}要好好利用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:56.20,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H264948&\frz343.871\pos(907,487)}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:56.20,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H264948&\frz258.769\pos(272,247)}姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:56.20,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H264948&\frz339.917\pos(265,322)}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.20,0:09:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\shad0\3c&H65618A&\c&H726FD4&\fad(300,0)}瑞 泽 高 中 GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.58,0:10:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊 西田!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.79,0:10:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有好好给你姐说明团体战的规则吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:09.54,writings3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}（从左到右）男生S码 女生L码 男生L码 男生M码 女生S码
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么设计的话 出场顺序岂不是只能有这一种了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.05,0:10:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外想问一下为什么选这顺序了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.01,0:10:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是按姐姐对样貌的喜欢顺序排的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.39,0:10:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最后一名?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒数第二?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.01,0:10:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,器用贫乏…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 第一名!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:31.98,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\c&HD2CEC9&\pos(1216,101)\frz265.173}是为什么呢\N 感觉有人看着…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:31.98,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H422878&\pos(920,209)\frz278.328}心跳不已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:31.98,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz277.885\pos(205,479)}锁定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:31.98,writings3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(217,529)}♪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为什么呢…感觉有人看着…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锁·定·♪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:37.36,subtitle_16_end,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(400,0)\c&H351B1F&}男生间的悄悄话①
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫濑和小奏…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做女朋友的话 哪个好?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我选小奏!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小奏…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真岛你太狡猾了! 快说啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用顾忌啦 你绝对也是选小奏的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.71,0:10:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫濑那种根本是不可能的吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.87,0:10:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs50\t(0,200,\fs30)\c&H4231C2&\3c&H353749&\shad0\a6}不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:53.38,writings3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H28231D&\pos(207,90)}做女朋友的话选谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:53.38,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H123332&\pos(618,495)}不可能 —
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.55,0:10:59.34,subtitle_16_end,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(400,0)\c&H351B1F&}男生间的悄悄话② — 太一反击篇 —
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:10:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是胸部吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.14,0:11:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是看上了大江同学的巨乳吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话我们可没说过啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乳…乳…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝言差矣!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小奏长得可爱 性格也好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟她去约会的情景是可以想象的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟绫濑的约会根本没法想象!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会变成去练习歌留多的!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:17.28,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}就是就是!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:19.53,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}说到底巨乳就是正义啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 绫濑绝对没门!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:24.66,writings3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H28231D&\pos(207,90)}做女朋友的话选谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:24.66,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H123332&\pos(622,469)}歌留多痴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是瑞泽高中的顺序表
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睫毛小子 睫毛小子!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原田老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说啦 你们打入决赛了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 太好了太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千早也在最佳状态吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从来都不知道 千早也会感到有压力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊? 千早也会?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为千早总是很强势
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我选择了错误的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然让她变得那么脆弱…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.74,0:12:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我居然连千早都不了解」…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.11,0:12:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须得接受这个事实对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.62,0:12:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我 是部长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为这样 所以我才一直注视着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「就算赌上全部青春 也不可能变得比新更强」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.68,0:12:23.84,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}回想起你们习惯的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.18,0:12:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在这里的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:25.72,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}没问题 绝对能行的!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.89,0:12:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是另外一个你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:28.89,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,かぜをいたみ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「万浪奔卷去…」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:31.89,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いまはただ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「苦恋不得允…」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.48,0:12:35.40,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,つくばねの…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.48,0:12:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「筑波男女川…」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫你不说「对不起」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抢到了!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抢到了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我抢到一张了! 太好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫濑 连我都能抢到敌阵的牌了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.71,0:12:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又怎么能在进攻上输给别人!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也抢到了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边守住了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:12:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下一张一定要抢到!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,个人战的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一张牌就只是一张牌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:17.36,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}こひぞつもりて　ふちとなりぬる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:17.36,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「情愫亦细始 历久成浩渊」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.44,0:13:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要为队伍抢下一张!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.11,0:13:18.52,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,わすらるる…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.11,0:13:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「海约已相违…」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:19.78,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,しらつゆに…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「秋色润原野…」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:21.15,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あはぢしま…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「鸻栖淡路岛…」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:22.90,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,みよしのの…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「秋风肃吉野…」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得漂亮 西田!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢指教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.79,0:13:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢指教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有决定字的变化我绝对不会弄错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.38,0:13:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要成为大家的支柱!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:47.18,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}いかにひさしき　ものとかはしる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:47.18,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「宵苦夜难尽 此艰君怎知」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯错这东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一张也不允许!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:50.93,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,よもすがら…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「意迷芳心乱…」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢指教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:13:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞泽一胜!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿下了!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿下了!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.95,0:14:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞泽两胜!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.84,0:14:22.59,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ちはやぶる…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.84,0:14:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「神代有蓬莱…」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸位!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.89,0:14:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一张一张地抢到手吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.17,0:15:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫濑弃权
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能输
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进攻…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.39,0:15:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要进攻…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能就这样结束的!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有比赛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.79,0:15:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早 你得躺着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛已经弃权了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弃权…?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,0:15:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早 都说不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老实呆着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了也没用 你已经回不去比赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明努力过了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.39,0:15:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟大家约好了…要赢下来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.28,0:16:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起 各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.11,0:16:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你这是做什么呢 千早
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.37,0:16:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么好道歉的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫濑 我今天第一次获胜了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 而且还是二连胜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.42,0:16:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然在复赛的淘汰赛中输给了富士崎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过好想再赛几场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.84,0:16:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身体状态不能马上恢复吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭明早第一班新干线回去如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到现在还按捺不住兴奋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对要恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以完美的身体状态迎战明天的个人赛!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若宫诗畅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是史上最年轻的女王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:48.94,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,はなさ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「山风…」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:53.07,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…そふ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「…邀樱散」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:16:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:16:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这战况 又来了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经差了十张了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.08,0:17:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若宫诗畅 果然等级不同啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女生也快丧失斗志了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早也不弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她应该能以不逊于女王的速度 抢下她盯上的牌的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.22,0:17:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是场上的牌有几十张
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.43,0:17:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法把全场的都盯住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…难道说女王能做到吗?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,办不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想象自己获胜的样子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事还是第一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不会手下留情的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只有那一张…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能在拼劲上 输给12岁时候的我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:52.71,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なにはえの…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「羁旅与君会…」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.01,0:17:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撞上了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:17:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说不相上下吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:04.02,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふくからに…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「枯风远山至…」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:09.11,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}ちはやぶる…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:09.11,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「神代有蓬莱…」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抢到了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20号抢到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直僵硬的身体 活动起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想变得更快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.21,0:18:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想变得更自如
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这竞技线当中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使面对强大得让身体都僵硬的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能自如地…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然难以表达
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但所谓「强大」就是这个意思!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢指教
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到头来…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:18:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只抢到了五张
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和女王的差距…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是二十张
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直线
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要笔直
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,0:19:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要笔直 要迅速…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗记必须更完美 不然使不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记住…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要记住…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.80,0:19:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要笔直 要迅速…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笔直 迅速…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细地听
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要更加 更加…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎样做才能赢她…?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎样做…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是今天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于在此刻…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早的梦…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化作了真正的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:56.50,subtitle_16_end,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(400,0)\c&H351B1F&}女生间的悄悄话①
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.21,0:19:56.50,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\move(685,109,681,109,0,480)\frz283.098\fad(400,0)}同班同学 \N小满
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说小千和小奏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.38,0:19:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要和歌留多部的其中一个人交往 你们会选谁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:19:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我想也用不着问啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要小奏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小奏 恭喜你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:05.89,subtitle_16_end,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs25\bord0\c&H322D28&\pos(461,52)}恭喜·独占鳌头!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.14,0:20:09.64,subtitle_16_end,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(400,0)\c&H351B1F&}女生间的悄悄话②
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.56,0:20:09.64,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\move(675,50,672,50,0,280)\frz283.098\fad(400,0)}想聊恋爱\N话题的小满
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦! 我问的是男生!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.18,0:20:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问要和男生交往的话会选谁!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不限于歌留多部也可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认真回答没问题吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.57,0:20:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.03,0:20:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊! 慢着!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会对正片造成影响的 你还是别说了!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.70,0:20:26.95,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H465052&\move(519,360,531,302)\frz262.448}后面还有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:26.95,writings4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz13.669\pos(178,429)}原
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:44.49,subtitle_16_end,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(400,0)}就算没在这个环节出场 我也不会在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.69,0:21:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新再用四字熟语描述一下对朋友的印象吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.98,0:21:44.49,subtitle_16,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H343434&\fs40\bord0\pos(740,418)\frz276.671}心无旁骛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次可别再说什么「烤肉套餐」了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}（感觉还是这个文言中\N表肯定的词最贴切…）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.74,0:21:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驹野啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.70,0:21:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「头脑明晰」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.70,0:21:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}头脑明晰（日语）：头脑灵活，才智出众
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小奏则是「才色兼备」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}才色兼备（日语）：有才华，\N有美貌，即才貌双全
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驹野同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.08,0:21:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长是…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「眉目秀丽」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}眉目秀丽（日语）：即眉清目秀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.05,0:22:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「猪突猛进」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.05,0:22:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}猪突猛进（日语）：指不考虑周围的人和情况，\N一味像猪一样以迅猛的势头前进
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.30,0:22:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这词足以概括千早了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.18,0:22:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.89,0:22:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.14,0:22:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉包小子是…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.56,0:22:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「养豚狗肉」?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.35,0:22:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬要说的话应该是「羊头狗肉」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.35,0:22:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}羊头狗肉（日语）：实质和外表不一致，\N即挂羊头卖狗肉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.86,0:22:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过为什么是这个熟语?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.86,0:22:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}「养豚」和「羊头」同音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.40,0:22:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为想不到其他的了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.44,0:22:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说绫濑你居然若无其事地说我是猪…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.44,0:22:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}日语中「豚」即指猪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.32,0:22:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是以上这些 今年也请多多指教咯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.78,0:22:34.99,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz279.268\pos(787,146)}我认为
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.78,0:22:34.99,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz279.268\pos(775,278)}无法记住全部百人一首的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.78,0:22:34.99,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz279.268\pos(732,241)}是虫豸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.78,0:22:34.99,writings4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz8.838\pos(831,463)\c&HE1CDFE&}须
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.87,0:22:34.99,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HE7E4E6&\frz260.236\move(317,432,337,342,0,120)\fad(100,0)}下周再见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.90,0:22:34.99,writings4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H535360&\frz349.184\pos(216,349)}浩
